column2: SELECT   p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,sp.modelMag_u,sp.modelMag_g,sp.modelMag_r,sp.modelMag_i,sp.modelMag_z,    (sp.modelMag_u-sp.modelMag_r) as &&&, (sp.modelMag_r-sp.modelMag_i) as &&&, (sp.modelMag_r-sp.modelMag_z) as &&&, (sp.modelMag_g-sp.modelMag_r) as &&&,   sp.class as obj_sp_type, sp.subclass as obj_sp_subtype, sp.z as redshift, em.bpt as em_sp_type, em.z as em_redshift, em.EW_Hb_# as Hb_EW, em.Flux_Hb_# as Hb_flux into mydb.dr1#_lcg_ports      from SpecPhoto AS sp, emissionLinesPort as em, PhotoObj as p        WHERE     sp.specobjid = em.specobjid     AND sp.objid = p.objid     AND em.EW_Hb_# > #
